      "title": "CPC trade unions to engage in protests tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Trade Unions of the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation (CPC) affiliated to all political parties are scheduled to engage in a protest march tomorrow against the proposed reforms of the CPC.",
        "Meanwhile, Power and Energy Minister Kanchana Wijesekera said that CPC reforms are a must and that he will continue to work to implement it.",
        "He said he had met all Trade Unions leaders to discuss the proposed reforms and conveyed its importance."
      ],
